data.description: The perfect blend of intown living and a beautiful neighborhood!  This gated community has well maintained common areas along with a playground and a community pool.  This sought after end unit townhome has an open concept living room, dining room and kitchen on the main floor with hardwoods.  Great for entertaining!  The upstairs has a large primary suite with a vaulted ceiling along with a large walk-in closet.  The primary en suite bathroom has double sinks and separate shower and tub.  Two big additional bedrooms along with a full bathroom and laundry are also on the second floor.  The private back patio has a nice wooded view and additional storage.  There is easy access to major transportation, work, schools, shopping and entertainment!
